						<div class="p-6 text-black dark:text-gray-300">
							<dt class="text-base font-medium leading-4 text-black dark:text-white">PWA support</dt>
							<p class="text-sm mt-2 text-black dark:text-gray-300">
								Progressive Web Apps are a new way to deliver amazing user experiences on the web. These are a great alternative to
								native apps.
							</p>

							<div class="mt-4 text-sm">
								<p>Benefits of a PWA:</p>

								<ul class="list-disc list-inside">
									<li>Offline support</li>
									<li>Push notifications</li>
									<li>Installable</li>
									<li>Fast access</li>
								</ul>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="p-6 break-words">
						<dt class="text-lg font-semibold leading-4 text-black dark:text-white">50$</dt>
						<p class="text-sm mt-2 text-black dark:text-gray-300">One-time fee</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-3 divide-x dark:divide-opacity-20 dark:divide-white">
					<div class="col-span-2 flex flex-col divide-y dark:divide-opacity-20 dark:divide-white">
						<div class="p-6 text-black dark:text-gray-300">
							<dt class="text-base font-medium leading-4 text-black dark:text-white">Content management system</dt>
							<p class="text-sm mt-2 text-black dark:text-gray-300">
								Looking for a way to manage your website content? We can integrate a CMS into your website.
							</p>

							<div class="mt-4 text-sm">
								<p>Why use a CMS?</p>

								<ul class="list-disc list-inside">
									<li>Easy to use</li>
									<li>Manage your content</li>
									<li>No need to contact us to make changes to your website.</li>
									<li>Great for blogs, news websites, and more.</li>
								</ul>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="p-6 break-words">
						<dt class="text-lg font-semibold leading-4 text-black dark:text-white">120$</dt>
						<p class="text-sm mt-2 text-black dark:text-gray-300">One-time fee</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-3 divide-x dark:divide-opacity-20 dark:divide-white">
					<div class="col-span-2 flex flex-col divide-y dark:divide-opacity-20 dark:divide-white">
						<div class="p-6 text-black dark:text-gray-300">
							<dt class="text-base font-medium leading-4 text-black dark:text-white">Analytics integration</dt>
							<p class="text-sm mt-2 text-black dark:text-gray-300">
								Want to know how your website is performing? We can integrate analytics into your website.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="p-6 break-words">
