								we can integrate a database into your website.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="p-6 break-words space-y-6">
						<div>
							<dt class="text-lg font-semibold leading-4 text-black dark:text-white">50$ + 70$ /mo</dt>
							<p class="text-sm mt-2 text-black dark:text-gray-300">Setup + hosting</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-3 divide-x dark:divide-opacity-20 dark:divide-white">
					<div class="col-span-2 flex flex-col divide-y dark:divide-opacity-20 dark:divide-white">
						<div class="p-6 text-black dark:text-gray-300">
							<dt class="text-base font-medium leading-4 text-black dark:text-white">User authentication</dt>
							<p class="text-sm mt-2 text-black dark:text-gray-300">
								Allow users to authenticate on your website with various methods.
							</p>

							<div class="flex mt-4 items-center">
								<div class="flex -space-x-1">
									<Image src={GoogleIcon} alt="Google" width={32} height={32} loading="eager" />
									<Image src={TwitterIcon} alt="Twitter" width={32} height={32} loading="eager" />
									<Image src={AppleIcon} alt="Apple" width={32} height={32} loading="eager" />
									<Image src={FacebookIcon} alt="Facebook" width={32} height={32} loading="eager" />
								</div>

								<b class="text-black dark:text-gray-300 text-xs ml-2">+ A dozen more</b>
							</div>
