					<div class="p-6 break-words space-y-6">
						<div>
							<dt class="text-lg font-semibold leading-4 text-black dark:text-white">50$</dt>
							<p class="text-sm mt-2 text-black dark:text-gray-300">One-time fee for each authentication method</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-3 divide-x dark:divide-opacity-20 dark:divide-white">
					<div class="col-span-2 flex flex-col divide-y dark:divide-opacity-20 dark:divide-white">
						<div class="p-6 text-black dark:text-gray-300">
							<dt class="text-base font-medium leading-4 text-black dark:text-white">Domain name management and registration</dt>
							<p class="text-sm mt-2 text-black dark:text-gray-300">
								If you don't have a domain name, we can register one for you. If you already have one, we can manage it for you.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="p-6 break-words space-y-6">
						<div>
							<dt class="text-lg font-semibold leading-4 text-black dark:text-white">50$</dt>
							<p class="text-sm mt-2 text-black dark:text-gray-300">
								One-time fee for domain name registration + 10$ /mo for domain name management
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-3 divide-x dark:divide-opacity-20 dark:divide-white">
					<div class="col-span-2 flex flex-col divide-y dark:divide-opacity-20 dark:divide-white">
						<div class="p-6 text-black dark:text-gray-300">
							<dt class="text-base font-medium leading-4 text-black dark:text-white">Email campaigns</dt>
							<p class="text-sm mt-2 text-black dark:text-gray-300">
								In case you want to send emails to your users, we can integrate an email campaign system into your website. You can
								setup email campaigns yourself or we can do it for you.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="p-6 break-words space-y-6">
						<div>
							<dt class="text-lg font-semibold leading-4 text-black dark:text-white">120$</dt>
							<p class="text-sm mt-2 text-black dark:text-gray-300">One-time fee</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-3 divide-x dark:divide-opacity-20 dark:divide-white">
					<div class="col-span-2 flex flex-col divide-y dark:divide-opacity-20 dark:divide-white">
						<div class="p-6 text-black dark:text-gray-300">
							<dt class="text-base font-medium leading-4 text-black dark:text-white">Asset management and content upload</dt>
							<p class="text-sm mt-2 text-black dark:text-gray-300">
								Allow users to upload content to your website. This can be useful for blogs, news websites, and more.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="p-6 break-words space-y-6">
						<div>
							<dt class="text-lg font-semibold leading-4 text-black dark:text-white">40$</dt>
							<p class="text-sm mt-2 text-black dark:text-gray-300">One-time fee</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
